OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1772048439
OL,3,CAll schools must provide SEN places
OL,4,Camid rising demand says Education
OL,5,CMinister
OL,7,FThe Education Minister has said all
OL,8,Fmainstream schools in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fwill be required to facilitate
OL,10,Fstudents with special educational
OL,11,Fneeds (SEN).
OL,13,FPaul Givan sent a letter to school
OL,14,Fprincipals saying "suitable" schools
OL,15,Fhave a role to play in meeting the
OL,16,Fneeds of children with SEN, which he
OL,17,Fdescribed as "one of the most pressing
OL,18,Fchallenges facing educational systems".
OL,26,@vD@SOUvD@\O]yD@NOUzD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/8
